description:
This is a 32 minute workout called '30 MIN PILATES FOR BEGINNERS || At-Home Mat Pilates (No Equipment)' from the channel Move With Nicole.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Masterclass Workout and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.
